  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "dprint jolt plugin configuration",
  "description": "Outer schema shape for dprint's `dprint.jsonc`: plugin options nested under the `jolt` config key, with all other dprint global keys permitted.\n\nThe field shape is supplied by `jolt_formatter::FormatOptions`, which uses camelCase keys (matching dprint's JSON convention) and carries the range constraints on `line_width`/`indent_width`.",
  "type": "object",
